title: My rank (GOLD)
body:
Dear Riot Games,

Just wondering why didn't i get my oriana skin, gold icon and gold border i hit gold before the season ended so i am a bit confused here


Kind regards,
Nangzz (OCE)

replies.body:
It may be your honor level, you need to be honor 2+ in order to get your rewards. If you aren't, it's ok because you have until [feb 11th](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/360011986113-2018-Season-Ranked-Reward-Eligibility-Update) to get to honor 2 and get those juicy rewards. 

Otherwise it could just be a delay in the rewards going out. There are millions of active accounts for the rewards to be distributed to and it can take a while for everything to go out. Riot has said that everyone currently eligible should have theirs by [december 12](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/360010365913-End-of-season-information) :)
